I've spoken with GIBrass (Jeff) and he has stock on these right now at $48 to $72 per 8 lb keg. These would come to me and I'd meet face-to-face with you for your share of the powder and actual final cost (keg price plus shipping-- divided by the number of total kegs bought; in cash). Oh... and let us not forget... you CAN'T GET the bulk canisters right now-- it's sold out nationwide for the better priced bulk canisters.

BUT there is a FOUR week delay on orders (even with Jeff, but at least he WILL ship it as he DOES have stock).
